      ******************************************************************
      * DCLGEN TABLE(INSURANCE_POLICY)                                 *
      *        LIBRARY(TECN347.PROJECT.DCLGEN(INSUR))                  *
      *        ACTION(REPLACE)                                         *
      *        LANGUAGE(COBOL)                                         *
      *        NAMES(HV1-)                                             *
      *        QUOTE                                                   *
      *        COLSUFFIX(YES)                                          *
      * ... IS THE DCLGEN COMMAND THAT MADE THE FOLLOWING STATEMENTS   *
      ******************************************************************
           EXEC SQL DECLARE INSURANCE_POLICY TABLE
           ( POLICY_ID                      CHAR(5) NOT NULL,
             POLICY_CODE                    CHAR(10),
             POLICY_NAME                    CHAR(25),
             POLICY_TYPE                    CHAR(10),
             POLICY_TERM                    CHAR(7),
             POLICY_AMNT                    CHAR(13)
           ) END-EXEC.
      ******************************************************************
      * COBOL DECLARATION FOR TABLE INSURANCE_POLICY                   *
      ******************************************************************
       01  DCLINSURANCE-POLICY.
      *                       POLICY_ID
           10 HV1-POLICY-ID        PIC X(5).
      *                       POLICY_CODE
           10 HV1-POLICY-CODE      PIC X(10).
      *                       POLICY_NAME
           10 HV1-POLICY-NAME      PIC X(25).
      *                       POLICY_TYPE
           10 HV1-POLICY-TYPE      PIC X(10).
      *                       POLICY_TERM
           10 HV1-POLICY-TERM      PIC X(7).
      *                       POLICY_AMNT
           10 HV1-POLICY-AMNT      PIC X(13).
      ******************************************************************
      * THE NUMBER OF COLUMNS DESCRIBED BY THIS DECLARATION IS 6       *
      ******************************************************************
